To download the documents in archive file:
а) Go to the documents list in Electronic archive menu;  б) ВTick the documents needed;  в) Press “download archive”; 
  г) Wait until the download status changes from “processing” to “finished” and press “open”;  д) Press “Download”; 
  The archive file will be downloaded to your computer.
